Symbol.Script_2D:
!! Design Table 02.gsm
unID=1
!!! ********************** Hotspots
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID : unID=unID+1
for i=1 to 4 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, temp_RR, 1+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, temp_RR, 3+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 temp_RR, 0, unID, temp_RR, 2, A: unID=unID+1
ROT2 90 next i DEL 3
!!! ********************** Minimal Space
call "fa_minimalspace" parameters all MSType = 7, unID = 3000
!!! ********************** 2D Symbol PEN gs_cont_pen FILL gs_fill_type POLY2_b 2, 1+2+4+64,gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0,901, a/2,360,4001
HOTARC2 0,0,A/2,0,180 HOTARC2 0,0,A/2,180,360
IF iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED THEN ROT2 45 LINE2 -a/2,0,a/2,0 LINE2 0,-a/2,0,a/2 DEL 1 ENDIF
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: iDet2D DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE = 1 DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2 DLEV3D_DRAFT = 3
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.` values{2} "iDet2D" DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED, `Детальный` VALUES "gs_resol" RANGE [3,)
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=4 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=19
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol" IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "temp_RR" then a = temp_RR * 2 b = temp_RR * 2 parameters a = a, b = b else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "B" then a = b temp_RR = b/2 parameters a = a, temp_RR = temp_RR else b = a temp_RR = a/2 parameters b = b, temp_RR = temp_RR endif endif
! --- Minimal Space ---
VALUES "MSFront" RANGE [0,)
